desc: TIMOI the brand, is a lifestyle artist brand with cute accessories, bags, apparel and prints. TIMOI the brand, comes from Graffiti Artist TIMOI, who grew up in Los Angeles and made her presence known there and now all over the world. TIMOI is an acronym for Trapped In My Own Imagination.

layout.text: ZOVEREIGNTY, GALAXY THE GREAT BY TIMOI

Join our community of Alien Big Eye Dolls called Huemans. They are creative angel like beings that come to earth to inspire humanity and protect the vulnerable. More than just a cute brand that offers art with utility, we are a community that is filled with creative and good hearted bad asses that look out for each other.
Join us!
